      <!-- Wallpaper Installation -->
      <div style="background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="color: #d4af37; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 600;">🗂️ Wallpaper Installation Tips</h3>
        <ul style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 15px; line-height: 2; margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
          <li><strong>Surface Preparation:</strong> Clean, smooth walls are essential for best results. Fill any holes and sand smooth.</li>
          <li><strong>Pattern Matching:</strong> All patterns repeat at 24" for seamless matching. Account for pattern repeat when ordering.</li>
          <li><strong>Tools Needed:</strong> Smoothing brush, utility knife, level, measuring tape, sponge, and clean water.</li>
          <li><strong>Application:</strong> Start from ceiling, match patterns carefully, smooth out air bubbles as you go.</li>
          <li><strong>Drying Time:</strong> Allow 24-48 hours for complete adhesion before painting trim or moving furniture.</li>
          <li><strong>Professional Help:</strong> Consider professional installation for best results, especially for large areas.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Fabric Care -->
      <div style="background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="color: #764ba2; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 600;">🧵 Fabric Care Instructions</h3>
        <ul style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 15px; line-height: 2; margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
          <li><strong>Cleaning:</strong> Professional cleaning recommended for upholstery to maintain color vibrancy and texture.</li>
          <li><strong>Washing:</strong> Spot clean only for most fabrics. Test in inconspicuous area first.</li>
          <li><strong>Stain Removal:</strong> Blot immediately, never rub. Use mild detergent solution for water-based stains.</li>
          <li><strong>Durability:</strong> All fabrics tested for residential use with proper care and maintenance.</li>
          <li><strong>Color Fastness:</strong> UV-resistant inks for long-lasting color. Avoid prolonged direct sunlight exposure.</li>
          <li><strong>Storage:</strong> Store rolled, not folded, in cool dry place if not using immediately.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

