        <h3 style="color: #e2e8f0; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 600;">How do I calculate how much I need?</h3>
        <p style="color: #a0aec0; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 15px; margin: 0;">
          <strong>For wallpaper:</strong> Measure wall height and width in feet, multiply to get square footage, then divide by roll coverage (54-60 sq ft). Add 10-15% extra for pattern matching and waste. Our customer service team can help with calculations.
          <br><br>
          <strong>For fabric:</strong> Measure the area you need to cover and add 10% for hems and adjustments. Consider pattern repeat if matching is required. Minimum order is 5 yards per fabric.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 30px; padding-bottom: 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
